comments: Thompson (DET) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Ayton (POR) prior to incidental contact occurring.
Camara (POR) initiates contact across Cunningham's (DET) right arm after Cunningham's gather, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Stewart (DET) is in Ayton's (POR) path and bracing for the impending contact as Ayton cuts toward him, which is marginal and absorbed by Stewart.
Camara (POR) is extending slightly as he firms up over his right foot and he does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the pick on Cunningham (DET).
Umude (DET) initiates contact with both of Sharpe's (POR) arms, affecting Sharpe's SQBR as he elevates.
Thompson (DET) establishes himself in Grant's (POR) path and does not deliver illegal contact as he slips to Grant's right side during the pick.
Grant (POR) is moving alongside Cunningham's (DET) path, and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Sharpe (POR) makes clean contact with the ball and deflects it away from Stewart (DET) during the rebound.
Camara (POR) and Stewart (DET) each make clean contact with the ball as simultaneous incidental arm contact occurs during the rebound.
Sasser (DET) initiates contact across Camara's (POR) arms prior to making any contact with the ball following the rebound.
Thompson (DET) establishes himself in Camara's (POR) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Brogdon (POR) and Harris (DET) briefly engage and disengage off-ball.

Stewart (DET) extends slightly as he firms up over his left foot and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the screen on Brogdon (POR). Cunningham (DET) is turning away from Brogdon and also does not deliver illegal contact as Brogdon attempts to move toward the perimeter.
Harris (DET) moves somewhat forward towards Brogdon (POR) and marginal contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Brogdon (POR) lowers his shoulder slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with Harris' (DET) front as they come together in the lane.
Grant (POR) legally contests Cunningham's (DET) jump shot attempt.
Harris (DET) steps slightly forward towards Brogdon (POR) and marginal contact occurs in the backcourt.
Cunningham (DET) commits a take foul on Sharpe (POR).
